# Build context is the repo root, but the server image only needs
# server/ + packages/contracts/. Keep the context small & the build
# reproducible by excluding everything else.

# The Flutter app is not part of the server image.
app/
project_activities_visualizer/

# Docs / notes
documents/
plans/
ux/
*.md
!server/README.md

# Dart/Flutter generated
**/.dart_tool/
**/build/
**/.packages
**/pubspec_lock_backup

# VCS / editor / OS
.git/
.github/
.idea/
.vscode/
.claude/
**/.DS_Store
*.swp
*.log
